msgctxt "sn56.51:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.51:0.2"
msgid "6. Abhisamayavagga "
msgstr "6. Comprehension "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.51:0.3"
msgid "51. Nakhasikhāsutta "
msgstr "51. A Fingernail "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.460, sc1
msgctxt "sn56.51:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā parittaṃ nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsuṃ āropetvā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha, picking up a little bit of dirt under his fingernail, addressed the mendicants: "

msgctxt "sn56.51:1.2"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "“What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn56.51:1.3"
msgid "katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ—yo vāyaṃ mayā paritto nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsu āropito, ayaṃ vā mahāpathavī”ti? "
msgstr "Which is more: the little bit of dirt under my fingernail, or this great earth?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.51:1.4"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ yadidaṃ—mahāpathavī; appamattakāyaṃ bhagavatā paritto nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsu āropito. "
msgstr "“Sir, the great earth is certainly more. The little bit of dirt under your fingernail is tiny. "

msgctxt "sn56.51:1.5"
msgid "Saṅkhampi na upeti, upanidhampi na upeti, kalabhāgampi na upeti mahāpathaviṃ upanidhāya bhagavatā paritto nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsu āropito”ti. "
msgstr "Compared to the great earth, it can’t be reckoned or compared, it’s not even a fraction.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.51:1.6"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa diṭṭhisampannassa puggalassa abhisametāvino etadeva bahutaraṃ dukkhaṃ yadidaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādinnaṃ; appamattakaṃ avasiṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr "“In the same way, for a person with comprehension, a noble disciple accomplished in view, the suffering that’s over and done with is more, what’s left is tiny. "

msgctxt "sn56.51:1.7"
msgid "Saṅkhampi na upeti, upanidhampi na upeti, kalabhāgampi na upeti purimaṃ dukkhakkhandhaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādinnaṃ upanidhāya yadidaṃ sattakkhattuparamatā; "
msgstr "Compared to the mass of suffering in the past that’s over and done with, it can’t be reckoned or compared, it’s not even a fraction, since there are at most seven more lives. "

msgctxt "sn56.51:1.8"
msgid "yo ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
msgstr "Such a person truly understands about suffering, its origin, its cessation, and the path. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn56.51:2.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.51:2.2"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

